'''Farrukh Sayfiyev'''  ({{lang-x2|uz|Farrux Sayfiyev|Фаррух Сайфиев}}; born 17 January 1991) is an Uzbek professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Full-back|left-back]] for [[FC Neftchi Fergana|Neftchi Fergana]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.worldfootball.net/person/pe364451/farrukh-sayfiyev/ |title=Farrukh Sayfiev |website=worldfootball.net |publisher=HEIM:SPIEL |access-date=24 December 2018}}</ref>

==Career==
On January 5, 2025, a member of the [[Uzbekistan Super League]], he signed a contract with the [[Fergana]] club Neftchi.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/neftchi-yana-bir-bomba-transferni-elon-qildi |title="Нефтчи" яна бир бомба трансферни эълон қилди |website=championat.asia |publisher=championat.asia |access-date=5 January 2025}}</ref>

===International===
Sayfiev made his debut for the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]] main team on 20 August 2014 in a [[Friendly (sport)|Friendly]] match against [[Azerbaijan national football team|Azerbaijan]].<ref>[https://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/11092/Azerbaijan_Uzbekistan.html Azerbaijan 0–0 Uzbekistan]</ref>

